WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:04.256
They wanted her piecemealed,
papier-mâchéd,

00:00:04.280 --> 00:00:08.096
practically broken,
limp-like and loveless,

00:00:08.119 --> 00:00:10.656
a litany of exaggeration.

00:00:10.680 --> 00:00:12.456
They wanted her low.

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:13.936
And high.

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:16.536
Flat and wide.

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:19.256
Filled with all of their empty.

00:00:19.280 --> 00:00:22.576
They wanted her to be more like them.

00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:25.336
Not knowing her conception was immaculate.

00:00:25.360 --> 00:00:28.496
That she was birthed
in sandalwood-scented river water,

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:30.576
sweet sapphire honey-touched tongue,